5
00:00:15,403 --> 00:00:18,036
The other way is by transmission.

6
00:00:18,356 --> 00:00:19,356
Yes.

7
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:22,349
I transmitted Leap Day to you two.

8
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:24,552
