18
00:00:42,465 --> 00:00:44,261
Would you rather we keep living like this?

19
00:00:44,950 --> 00:00:47,090
Would you rather we keep letting people die for us?

20
00:00:49,590 --> 00:00:50,960
Use your head!

21
00:00:51,990 --> 00:00:53,221
Yeah!

22
00:00:54,378 --> 00:00:56,330
At least we’ll be able to keep who we love safe!

23
00:00:56,363 --> 00:00:57,963
Who cares what’s become of other people?

24
00:00:59,534 --> 00:01:01,374
You wanna save everyone else

25
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,138
