It’s alright.

107
00:06:21,847 --> 00:06:22,847
Just go.

108
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,694
Alright.

109
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:24,785
Bye, Dad.

110
00:06:25,701 --> 00:06:26,640
Goodbye.

111
