126
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,334
No building a family.

127
00:07:28,370 --> 00:07:29,323
No future.

128
00:07:29,352 --> 00:07:30,676
Just a promise of a lonely death.

129
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:33,112
You save everyone,

130
00:07:33,134 --> 00:07:34,785
except the ones you love.

131
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,360
It’s this room.

132
00:08:25,570 --> 00:08:27,025
