133
00:08:27,054 --> 00:08:28,269
I’m here with him.

134
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,090
We can talk, too.

135
00:08:34,090 --> 00:08:34,923
You had breakfast?

136
00:08:34,952 --> 00:08:35,952
I bought you some congee.

137
00:08:37,660 --> 00:08:38,785
